---
// About.astro - Static component for the about section
---

<section id="about">
	<div class="about-grid">
		<div class="about-copy">
			<p class="section-kicker">About</p>
			<h2>Calm under pressure, curious by default.</h2>
			<p class="intro">
				I'm Sam, a computer science student at the University of South Florida. I am drawn to work where
				reliability matters: debugging, support tooling, data analysis, and systems that need to be understood
				before they can be improved.
			</p>
			<p class="intro">
				Outside of class and internships, I compete in collegiate esports, help lead professional development
				for SHPE, and keep coming back to projects that mix software with real-world constraints.
			</p>
		</div>

		<aside class="identity-panel" aria-label="Personal notes">
			<div class="panel-top">
				<span class="tiny-label">Current frequency</span>
				<strong>Enterprise systems / competitive play / applied projects</strong>
			</div>
			<div class="notes">
				<span>USF Computer Science</span>
				<span>Collegiate esports player</span>
				<span>Former professional development director</span>
				<span>Professional dev and team mentorship</span>
			</div>
			<div class="interest-space">
				<div class="interest-mark">01</div>
				<p>Room for a future photo, setup shot, match-day detail, or another personal artifact.</p>
			</div>
		</aside>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	#about {
		max-width: 1120px;
		padding-top: 2rem;
	}

	.about-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(300px, 0.55fr);
		gap: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 5rem);
		align-items: stretch;
	}

	#about h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.section-kicker,
	.tiny-label {
		color: var(--accent-2);
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--soft);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.identity-panel {
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-radius: 8px;
		background:
			linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(196, 243, 106, 0.08), transparent 45%),
			var(--ink-2);
		padding: 1.2rem;
	}

	.panel-top {
		padding-bottom: 1.2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
	}

	.panel-top strong {
		display: block;
		color: var(--paper);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.25;
	}

	.notes {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.55rem;
		padding: 1.2rem 0;
	}

	.notes span {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.interest-space {
		min-height: 10.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: space-between;
		border: 1px dashed var(--line-strong);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1rem;
	}

	.interest-mark {
		color: var(--accent-3);
		font-size: 2.6rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.interest-space p {
		color: var(--dim);
		font-size: 0.88rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 820px) {
		.about-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
